closer to us, and

45
00:02:57,977 --> 00:03:03,600
that objects that appear smaller than
other objects must be farther away.

46
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:07,260
That's a size constancy
expectation we have, and

47
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:10,570
